---
description: Prevent modal dropdown clipping in viewport
globs: frontend/src/views/**/*.vue
alwaysApply: false
---

# Modal Dropdown Viewport Safety

- For dropdowns inside modal cards, keep dropdown options opening below the field.
- Use a positioned field wrapper and a custom dropdown panel with:
  - `position: absolute`
  - `top: calc(100% + 6px)`
  - `max-height` + `overflow-y: auto`
  - explicit `z-index` above modal content
- For modal sections containing dropdowns, use the same non-clipping card classes used by existing modal filter UIs:
  - `class="auth-card modal-card mention-host-card filter-modal-card"`
- Do not add flip-up behavior for modal dropdowns unless explicitly requested.
- Avoid browser-native `datalist` for modal dropdowns when consistent placement and keyboard behavior are required.
